DISCRIMINATION; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; HEALTH INSURANCE; CIVIL RIGHTS; EMPLOYEE 
RIGHTS; PRIVACY; MEDICAL ETHICS; CONFIDENTIALITY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
