NAMIBIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SOUTH AFRICA; SOUTH AFRICA -- TERRITORIES AND 
POSSESSIONS; UNITED NATIONS -- NAMIBIA; SOVEREIGNTY; SOUTH WEST AFRICA PEOPLE'S 
ORGANIZATION 
</P>
