PALESTINE NATIONAL COUNCIL; FRANCE -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; ISRAEL -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; MIDDLE EAST PEACE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
