EUROPE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EUROPE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; EUROPE -- DEFENSE; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; MISSILE 
SITES; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- EUROPE; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; ARMS CONTROL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
