<DATELINE>
<P>
SALT SPRINGS, Fla. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jim and Tammy Faye Bakker have moved into a retreat for "tired" ministers and 
will broadcast their religious television show from the 29-acre compound, the 
retreat's director said today. 
</P>
<P>
"Temporarily, they're staying with us," said Duane Starr at the Lake George 
Ministries Retreat. "Three weeks, a couple weeks, a week. They're looking to 
relocate. This is just short-term, in between." 
</P>
